---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="示例概念 — AI PM 工作台" description="探索通过工作台结构化的真实 AI 产品想法" lang="zh-CN">
  <div class="space-y-6">
    <div class="mb-10">
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-3">示例概念</h1>
      <p class="text-muted-foreground max-w-2xl">探索通过工作台结构化的真实 AI 产品想法。点击任意示例，在工作台中打开并预填所有字段。</p>
      <p class="text-xs text-muted-foreground/70 mt-2">以下为使用模拟假设构建的示例。真实项目中的指标与目标需要另行验证。</p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-3">
      <!-- Card 1: Prompt-to-Ontology -->
      <div class="bg-card rounded-xl ring-1 ring-foreground/10 p-6 flex flex-col">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-3">
          <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold" style="background: oklch(0.45 0.15 160 / 0.2); color: oklch(0.75 0.15 160);">1</div>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold">Prompt-to-Ontology</h2>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground mb-4 flex-1">通过 AI 辅助的 schema 提取，将零散的业务概念转化为结构化的本体资产。适合企业知识管理产品。</p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-4">
          <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-secondary text-xs text-muted-foreground">本体知识</span>
          <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-secondary text-xs text-muted-foreground">schema 提取</span>
        </div>
        <a href="/AI-PM-Workbench/zh-CN/workbench/" onclick="sessionStorage.setItem('ai-pm-load-example','prompt-to-ontology')" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-sm font-medium text-emerald-400 hover:text-emerald-300 transition-colors">
          在工作台中打开
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7l5 5-5 5M6 12h12"/></svg>
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 2: Industrial Agent Decision Support -->
      <div class="bg-card rounded-xl ring-1 ring-foreground/10 p-6 flex flex-col">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-3">
          <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold" style="background: oklch(0.55 0.15 200 / 0.2); color: oklch(0.75 0.15 200);">2</div>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold">工业智能体决策支持</h2>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground mb-4 flex-1">通过 AI 辅助的多步骤工作流诊断制造设备问题。结合传感器数据、维护历史和工程知识。</p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-4">
          <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-secondary text-xs text-muted-foreground">智能体</span>
          <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-secondary text-xs text-muted-foreground">工业 AI</span>
        </div>
        <a href="/AI-PM-Workbench/zh-CN/workbench/" onclick="sessionStorage.setItem('ai-pm-load-example','industrial-agent')" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-sm font-medium text-emerald-400 hover:text-emerald-300 transition-colors">
          在工作台中打开
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7l5 5-5 5M6 12h12"/></svg>
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 3: RAG Knowledge Assistant -->
      <div class="bg-card rounded-xl ring-1 ring-foreground/10 p-6 flex flex-col">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-3">
          <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold" style="background: oklch(0.6 0.15 260 / 0.2); color: oklch(0.75 0.15 260);">3</div>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold">RAG 知识助手</h2>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground mb-4 flex-1">利用检索增强生成帮助员工从内部文档中查找答案。基于公司 Wiki、政策文件和项目文档。</p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-4">
          <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-secondary text-xs text-muted-foreground">RAG</span>
          <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-secondary text-xs text-muted-foreground">知识获取</span>
        </div>
        <a href="/AI-PM-Workbench/zh-CN/workbench/" onclick="sessionStorage.setItem('ai-pm-load-example','rag-assistant')" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-sm font-medium text-emerald-400 hover:text-emerald-300 transition-colors">
          在工作台中打开
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7l5 5-5 5M6 12h12"/></svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
